parameters:
????: Upon receiving the report of an intruder and rushing
over... I see, it was you after all.

Mage in Robes: I had a feeling we'd meet again soon, but to
think you'd come alone. Kukukuku...!

You're the sorcerer who set the golems loose in the
reconstruction district...!!

Mage in Robes: This is perfect. I'll return the favor from
the town. And to ensure you never interfere with us again,
I'll finish you off right here today!
Mage in Robes: Don't think you can win this time either!!

Mage in Robes: Minions, attack!! Do not let that woman
escape!!

Hmph, I was prepared for battle from the start! I won't
start getting cold feet now!!

(It seems there are many enemies, but fortunately, this
corridor is narrow.)

(But poor visibility goes both ways. If I can get behind
their rank and file, I should be able to launch a surprise
attack.)

(They may intend to overwhelm with numbers, but if there's
no worry of being surrounded from all sides, then I just
need to cut down those who stand before me!!)

You'd better brace yourself! Today, you'll be the one
showing off your pathetic attempt to flee!!
